  audioProfileName: SunSworn History 3
  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Although mana could grant sentience to anything it touched, it did
      not grant intelligence or wisdom.  Fire elementals would burn everything around
      them.
    nextOption: 
  - startTime: 10
    showTime: 10
    description: Likewise, the dead would come back to life with an eternal grudge
      against everyone.
    nextOption: 
  - startTime: 20
    showTime: 10
    description: Wars tore the world apart and threatened to destroy it until the
      SunDancer twins created the SunSworn with the goal of banning magic use and
      protecting the world from harm.
    nextOption: 
  - startTime: 30
    showTime: 10
    description: They amassed an army of followers, and tried to convince everyone
      to abandon their harmful ways.  Not everyone agreed and there were many battles.
    nextOption: 
